social_posts.post_text: I believe in a thing called looooove!!!

Of course one of the most fun people I know throws one of the most fun weddings I’ve ever been to. It was hard to pick only 10 photos for this day, but I feel like they do a good job of explaining what happened. Congratulations @babbydeeter & @__ftb!! (Honorable mention to @courtneybrano for picking up my homeless ass)
Need more time above tree line STAT @kristinnanderson
So a year ago I ran the New York City Marathon and failed at the most important part of running a marathon. Posting it for social media glory. Oh, and @tracymorgan is my best friend now.
2022 @lcdsoundsystem @brooklynsteel run. Even after nearly a year I still feel that 12/16/22 was the best concert I’ve been to, of all time, ever.
When @kikiluke5 says “come to Ultra Miami and meet my friends” you say yes and get to pedaling. Florida coast: ✅

@ultra was my first music festival ever, back when I was 16. My 16th birthday present from my parents wasn’t a car, wasn’t a ticket to ultra, it was permission to go. Best gift ever. Fast forward a few years and… idk… 50(?) festivals; we back. 📸 by me.
When your sister that’s not actually your sister gets married you pull out all the moves. So happy for you @thathanhilp & @juhilpy! (If you invite me to your wedding I WILL dance with your mom)
